data.text:
Continuing with the minisode storyline, TOMORROW X TOGETHER (TXT) is back with a new mini album titled minisode 3: TOMORROW now in the Light Ver. Available in 5 versions specific to each member: SOOBIN, YEONJUN, BEOMGYU, TAEHYUN and HUENINGKAI. Contents of the album include: Package Box, Album Stand, CD, CD Envelope, Postcard set (23 postcards), Lyric Card Set, Mini Poster, Photocard (random 1 of 5) and Sticker. Dimensions: 175 x 130 x 22 mm.

Click here for detailed package image.

Available for US customers only. This product is only available to customers using both a U.S. billing and shipping address for their order. Ineligible orders will be canceled.
